---
permalink: /a11y/
title: Accessibility 
description: "The New York State Design System makes it easier to build accessible, mobile-friendly applications and websites for New York State."
crawl: false
site_nav: false
heading_links: false
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
<!-- Home Hero -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero__inner">
    <div class="hero__content">
      <svg width="209" height="13" viewBox="0 0 209 13" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <rect x="104.33" width="52.1654" height="12.9576" fill="#FACE00"/>
        <rect x="156.498" width="52.1654" height="12.9576" fill="#0E324F"/>
        <rect x="52.166" width="52.1654" height="12.9576" fill="#004DD1"/>
        <rect width="52.1654" height="12.9576" fill="#A2350A"/>
      </svg>
      <h1>Be an <span class="heavy">a11y.</span></h1>
      <p>Accessible design is better for everyone.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__media">
      <img src="{{ '/assets/img/a11y-banner.png' | url }}" alt="">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.hero *,
.a11y-card * {
  color: var(--nys-color-theme-strong);
}

@media (width > 1024px) {
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 96px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: var(--nys-space-200);
    margin-bottom: var(--nys-space-100);
  }
}

@media (width <= 1024px) {
  .hero__inner {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
}
.hero p {
  font-size: var(--nys-font-size-3xl);
}

.hero h1,
.hero p,
.a11y-card h3,
.a11y-card p {
  font-family: 'Atkinson Hyperlegible Next', sans-serif;
  font-weight: normal;
}

.heavy {
  font-weight: 600;
}

.a11y-card p {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
}
</style>

<div class="nys-top-800 nys-padding-y-800">
  <div class="nys-grid-container-widescreen">
    <div class="nys-grid-row nys-grid-gap-6 nys-flex-justify-center">
      <div class="a11y-card nys-tablet:nys-grid-col-7 nys-desktop:nys-grid-col-3 nys-display-flex nys-flex-column nys-margin-b-200">
        <img src="/assets/img/a11y-grid-artboard-4-80.jpg" style="clip-path: polygon(7% 7%, 93% 5%, 91% 95%, 5% 87%)">
        <div class="nys-grid-row">
          <div class="nys-grid-col-10 nys-grid-offset-1">
            <h3><span class="heavy">a11y</span> is short for <span class="heavy">accessibility</span>.</h3>
            <p>There are 11 letters between the <span class="heavy">a</span> and <span class="heavy">y</span>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="a11y-card nys-tablet:nys-grid-col-7 nys-desktop:nys-grid-col-3 nys-display-flex nys-flex-column nys-margin-b-200">
        <img src="/assets/img/a11y-grid-artboard-5-80.jpg" style="clip-path: polygon(3% 0%, 96% 3%, 94% 92%, 5% 99%)">
        <div class="nys-grid-row">
          <div class="nys-grid-col-10 nys-grid-offset-1">
            <h3><span class="heavy">Inclusion</span> isn't optional.</h3>
            <p>Over 1 billion people globally live with a disability, including <span class="heavy">nearly 1 in 4 New Yorkers.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="a11y-card nys-tablet:nys-grid-col-7 nys-desktop:nys-grid-col-3 nys-display-flex nys-flex-column nys-margin-b-200">
        <img src="/assets/img/a11y-grid-artboard-6-80.jpg" style="clip-path: polygon(1% 10%, 98% 8%, 99% 98%, 0% 96%)">
        <div class="nys-grid-row">
          <div class="nys-grid-col-10 nys-grid-offset-1">
            <h3>Compliance matters. <span class="heavy">People matter more.</span></h3>
            <p>Helping New Yorkers access public services is more than just meeting legal requirements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="nys-grid-row nys-grid-gap-6 nys-flex-justify-center">
      <div class="a11y-card nys-tablet:nys-grid-col-7 nys-desktop:nys-grid-col-3 nys-display-flex nys-flex-column nys-margin-b-200">
        <img src="/assets/img/a11y-grid-artboard-7-80.jpg" style="clip-path: polygon(0% 11%, 100% 9%, 96% 86%, 47% 83%, 47% 93%, 14% 96%, 13% 82%, 2% 81%);
">
        <div class="nys-grid-row">
          <div class="nys-grid-col-10 nys-grid-offset-1">
            <h3><span class="heavy">Champions</span> of <span class="heavy">inclusion.</span></h3>
            <p>The ITS Accessibility Team partners with dedicated NYS teams to make digital services accessible for every New Yorker.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="a11y-card nys-tablet:nys-grid-col-7 nys-desktop:nys-grid-col-3 nys-display-flex nys-flex-column nys-margin-b-200">
        <img src="/assets/img/a11y-grid-artboard-8-80.jpg" style="clip-path: polygon(5% 7%, 96% 5%, 94% 91%, 6% 84%);">
        <div class="nys-grid-row">
          <div class="nys-grid-col-10 nys-grid-offset-1">
            <h3><span class="heavy">Brains</span> work <span class="heavy">differently.</span></h3>
            <p>Words and design that are clear and simple work better for everyone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="a11y-card nys-tablet:nys-grid-col-7 nys-desktop:nys-grid-col-3 nys-display-flex nys-flex-column nys-margin-b-200">
        <img src="/assets/img/a11y-grid-artboard-9-80.jpg" style="clip-path: polygon(8% 12%, 95% 5%, 95% 92%, 6% 92%);">
        <div class="nys-grid-row">
          <div class="nys-grid-col-10 nys-grid-offset-1">
            <h3><span class="heavy">Accessibility</span> is a <span class="heavy">right.</span></h3>
            <p>When we build digital services that are inclusive, we effectively serve all New Yorkers with compassion, dignity, and equity</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="nys-grid-row nys-grid-gap-6 nys-flex-justify-center">
      <div class="a11y-card nys-tablet:nys-grid-col-7 nys-desktop:nys-grid-col-3 nys-display-flex nys-flex-column nys-margin-b-200">
        <img src="/assets/img/a11y-grid-artboard-1-80.jpg" style="clip-path: polygon(7% 5%, 98% 10%, 97% 93%, 4% 95%);">
        <div class="nys-grid-row">
          <div class="nys-grid-col-10 nys-grid-offset-1">
            <h3><span class="heavy">Sound</span> isn't always <span class="heavy">heard.</span></h3>
            <p>Captions and transcripts make content work for everyone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="a11y-card nys-tablet:nys-grid-col-7 nys-desktop:nys-grid-col-3 nys-display-flex nys-flex-column nys-margin-b-200">
        <img src="/assets/img/a11y-grid-artboard-2-80.jpg" style="clip-path: polygon(2% 8%, 95% 3%, 97% 95%, 2% 94%);">
        <div class="nys-grid-row">
          <div class="nys-grid-col-10 nys-grid-offset-1">
            <h3><span class="heavy">Accessibility</span> should be <span class="heavy">everywhere.</span></h3>
            <p>Accessible design is usable by everyone — regardless of ability, age, or circumstance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="a11y-card nys-tablet:nys-grid-col-7 nys-desktop:nys-grid-col-3 nys-display-flex nys-flex-column nys-margin-b-200">
        <img src="/assets/img/a11y-grid-artboard-3-80.jpg" style="clip-path: polygon(8% 7%, 93% 6%, 94% 92%, 6% 86%);">
        <div class="nys-grid-row">
          <div class="nys-grid-col-10 nys-grid-offset-1">
            <h3>Compliance matters. <span class="heavy">People matter more.</span></h3>
            <p>Helping New Yorkers access public services is more than just meeting legal requirements.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <img src="{{ '/assets/img/poster-58.png' | url }}" alt="" role="presentation">
    <img src="{{ '/assets/img/poster-60.png' | url }}" alt="" role="presentation">
    <img src="{{ '/assets/img/poster-61.png' | url }}" alt="" role="presentation">
  </div>
</div>

{% endblock %}

